# Whenever working with the database

- Review the schema file [schema.sql](mdc:interface/modules/custom_modules/air-liquide-module/schema.sql) for the database structure
- Please use sqlStatement, sqlQuery, sqlInsert (etc) when making database calls.  You can see examples of this in [slots.php](mdc:interface/modules/custom_modules/air-liquide-module/api/engage/slots.php).
- The identification column in patient_data is "pid"
- Never create new databases with foreign keys.  Only use indexed integer columns.
